# ğŸŒ **Who We Are**

**Desert Stream Partners International (DESPI)** is an indigenous African missions agency called and commissioned to glorify God among the unreached and the least-reached peoples of Africa, especially within the Muslim world.

We are a **faith-based ministry**, wholly anchored on biblical truth and dependent on God for direction, provision, and sustainability.

Our calling is to bring the life-giving message of Christ into the spiritual â€œdesertsâ€ of the world â€” transforming hearts, communities, and nations through the power of the gospel.

We began our journey from Nigeria to Sudan, and continue to extend the light of Christ to the ends of the earth.

